part_description = "[b]H GUIDED MISSILES (QTY: 3 // DMG: 4)[/b]
[b]Speed:[/b] 3 in any direction.
[b]Guided:[/b] Does not have to designate a target when Deployed. Can choose to have Guided missiles attack any target at range 0. Increase the number to shoot down by 1.
[b]Crit:[/b] Hit every adjacent square for 1 DMG."
